<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">( <span class="c4">[٢٨]</span> )</span> في صحيحه <span class="c2">(٤/١٨٨)</span> وانظر: -أيضاً - فتح المغيث <span class="c2">(٤/٧٧)</span> .<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
